{"tid":1019801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張家輝涉特賣場偷32元電子貨品  否認盗竊4月開審","createTime":"2019-02-13T07:33:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T05:32:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3d616d622b377794be2edcda35fe906ede3a0c5d","tid":1019801,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:33:56.000Z","msg":"駐守‪九龍城分區‬休班警長去年5月，涉嫌在深水埗‪電子特賣城‬內偷竊數件總值32元的貨品。警長今在西九龍裁判法院否認一項盗竊罪，裁判官將案排期至4月1日開審，審期一天。控方料將傳召5名證人和庭上播放相關的閉路電視片段；被告則可能會傳召一名醫生證人抗辯。<br />\n<br />\n51歲被告張家輝被控於去年5月18日，在‪深水埗福仁商場電子特賣城‬盜竊一個小型多功能包（價值9元），一塊行李牌（價值5元），一盞LED燈（價值15元）及一包眼鏡防滑貼（價值3元），總值32元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1431717/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1431717%2F&d=IVQfIEXj%2BCIGzEn528CwiQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=749da0ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1431717%2F&h=74d00af0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1431717/</a>"},{"pid":"7aff05518859344fd2a1a0067110ff1645eb6f0c","tid":1019801,"uid":17081,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/160739_65ede9ce3289c08371863eab3b9f882f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F160739_65ede9ce3289c08371863eab3b9f882f.png&h=69315b7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6d14270ad83389aa55a75fb525bed3c26619b42","tid":1019801,"uid":52459,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:24:06.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係衰偷拍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/02/13/161335_35f18d907102e0de7d310f13b7e22123.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F02%2F13%2F161335_35f18d907102e0de7d310f13b7e22123.png&h=6665cbae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1605f82fe74400c4b5465f4a8a886fe6a8a91aa","tid":1019801,"uid":52881,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:35:44.000Z","msg":"休班警加一分<br />\n<br />\n好偷唔偷,走去褔仁個特賣場偷埋D咁嘅野<br />\n講出來都怕俾人笑啦"},{"pid":"a3fb9179631176f13ad4789cbc912ec3ee0e8e5f","tid":1019801,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"張家輝咁得閒成日偷野"},{"pid":"3e6cb6c4aec1bbc8ff2077e6602fae35ac1c90b3","tid":1019801,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5949665e5b8eef310fe9fc3906dc303b966f779a","tid":1019801,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"7aff05518859344fd2a1a0067110ff1645eb6f0c","tid":1019801,"uid":17081,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/160739_65ede9ce3289c08371863eab3b9f882f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F160739_65ede9ce3289c08371863eab3b9f882f.png&h=69315b7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:47:15.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，小偷變魔？咁徐步高係乜？"},{"pid":"bad4167b4f2f2fbb36a8f8cfd8983b645a49db74","tid":1019801,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"福仁檔野都好偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8b2dc8b8ad98d62fab7d161fd972be93c3deba","tid":1019801,"uid":46538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:48:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母標題黨"},{"pid":"77f91b094ea86d14df768ba11194ae92aab0b421","tid":1019801,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:49:46.000Z","msg":"渣渣輝"},{"pid":"3a7a6cd428dfcab0a46d89179e271b6560b07fbc","tid":1019801,"uid":103156,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"被告警長張家輝：(Apple Daily)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQZPuc7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQZPuc7.png&h=58f73e50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1601cc40aafa245c6136367bb3f5f8bd403fa68e","tid":1019801,"uid":23120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"警隊雜項調查小隊一名警長涉替一名女子出頭，向按摩院女店東撻朵，逼對方退還頂手費的5,000元定金，或減價將按摩院出讓，帶同事巡查時更威脅女店東：「你仲做呀？我搞你㗎！」警長被控兩項公職人員行為失當罪受審。<br />\n被告張家輝（51歲，圖）案發時駐守九龍城分區雜項調查小隊，職責包括巡查按摩院及放蛇。兩項公職人員行為失當罪指他於2014年3月18日休班期間，向女事主廖秀麗表露警員身份及施壓；另於同年7月4日及25日，威脅若廖繼續經營該按摩院，便會騷擾廖。<br />\n2009年來港的廖供稱，2013年10月尾在九龍城打鼓嶺道開設沐足店「樂足樂」，翌年2月放盤出讓店舖。後來一名叫王傳蘭的女子來問價，3月6日落實頂手費12.8萬元，王先付5,000元定金。雙方並簽訂協議，講明王若反悔會遭殺定。<br />\n<br />\n查牌時恐嚇「我搞你㗎」 <br />\n廖指，翌日王嫌貴反口，要求退定或減價，廖拒絕，二人爭吵。她指王稱妹夫做政府工，「認識很多差人」，恐嚇她若不答應，便要「搞到我舖頭開唔落去」。<br />\n控方開案指，同月18日晚，被告休班時到廖的按摩院，要廖退定或減價讓王頂手，否則不要在九龍城繼續經營按摩院。廖質問被告與王是甚麼關係及為何幫王出頭，被告自言是警察，並展示警察證件。<br />\n至7月25日晚上9時，被告與同事到該店例行查牌，其間被告向廖稱「你仲做呀？我搞你㗎！」同樣事情在7月4日也曾發生。兩個月後，被告和同袍到店放蛇，指該店違例，未領牌照下替異性顧客全身按摩。<br />\n廉署調查顯示，被告毋須參與有關足浴店的調查工作或處理金錢糾紛，亦從未被指派在公餘時間到任何足浴店執行職務。2015年10月被告被捕，警誡下承認因公務認識廖，但否認識王。<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1024/17"},{"pid":"db90e8e1ad86f9ca196a762fe5f0281cad005818","tid":1019801,"uid":1713,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3a7a6cd428dfcab0a46d89179e271b6560b07fbc","tid":1019801,"uid":103156,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"被告警長張家輝：(Apple Daily)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQZPuc7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQZPuc7.png&h=58f73e50&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:21:50.000Z","msg":"有d 似<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c6a6fe3019f5e3109a6844238f7f50ca9f473d6","tid":1019801,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"佢係會員老貓再世_"},{"pid":"043615aca30f675b46a22cb25c33a982f9cde4f5","tid":1019801,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c6a6fe3019f5e3109a6844238f7f50ca9f473d6","tid":1019801,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:23:12.000Z","msg":"佢係會員老貓再世_"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T09:24:48.000Z","msg":"做警長咁撚巴閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfda3868a0b8eb1edeac32bfe4e49a33a8e9f1d","tid":1019801,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cff77846b8b76e5c9ba397cf5c231189f067e3","tid":1019801,"uid":146537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"我是渣渣輝"},{"pid":"db591253b83ca0cb56a5b116240286e31d2f916f","tid":1019801,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87ad1497be6387be9d9cecd30704d9dc1e117d9","tid":1019801,"uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">被告則可能會傳召一名醫生證人抗辯</span><br />\n<br />\n真係識玩，到時話自己精神有問題又走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}